Installation Instructions
*************************

~/libsyslogpp $ mkdir build
~/libsyslogpp $ cd build
~/libsyslogpp/build $ cmake ..

On Debian or with RPM run:
~/libsyslogpp/build $ make package

And install the result packages

On other OS:
~/libsyslogpp/build $ make
~/libsyslogpp/build $ sudo make install # `make deinstall' is not supported

